dct_description_sm: This collection contains shapefiles representing key statistics from the 2012 Census of Bolivia (Censo Nacional de Población y Vivienda 2012). The original questionairre and other documentation is included with each download.
System requirements: Geographic Information Systems (GIS) software that reads ESRI shapefile format.
dct_creator_sm: Bolivia, Dirección Nacional de Estadística y Censos
